                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The use of "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "READ UNCOMMITTED",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " may result in reading uncommitted changes, which could lead to inconsistencies in the report data."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Parameter Sensitivity",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure's behavior changes based on the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@IsAgencyUser",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " flag, which could lead to unexpected results if not properly understood or documented."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Scalability",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": As the data grows, the performance of the joins and subqueries might degrade if not optimized with appropriate indexing and query tuning."
                }
              ]
